comments: Theis (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during the drive to the basket by Antetokounmpo (MIL) and marginal contact occurs after Antetokounmpo drives past him.
Holiday (MIL) makes marginal contact with Walker's (BOS) arm and does not affect his control of the ball during his drive.

Replay review of the offensive foul called on Antetokounmpo (MIL) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Theis (BOS) is in a legal guarding position in Antetokounmpo's path and Antetokounmpo initiates contact with his elbow extended.
Middleton (MIL) slightly extends his arms into Theis' (BOS) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Theis (BOS) makes marginal contact with Middleton (MIL) as he slightly extends his arms into his body during the pick and does not affect his ability to defend.
Brown (BOS) makes marginal contact with Middleton's (MIL) body and does not dislodge him in the backcourt.
Smart (BOS) makes lower body contact with Middleton (MIL) while he is airborne that affects his jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) briefly grasps Lopez's (MIL) arm and does not affect his FOM during the rebound.
DiVincenzo (MIL) cleanly blocks Walker (BOS) during his driving shot attempt. Any arm contact after the block is deemed incidental.
Smart (BOS) goes to deflect the pass and marginal contact occurs with Lopez (MIL).
Holiday (MIL) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Smart (BOS) during his drive.
Middleton (MIL) and Brown (BOS) make incidental contact with each other off ball.
Lopez (MIL) cleanly blocks Smart's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Walker (BOS) makes marginal contact with DiVincenzo (MIL) and does not dislodge him during the screen.
Middleton (MIL) cleanly deflects the incoming pass from Brown (BOS).
